title: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: When exporting data from a table that contains highlight or map, an exception is thrown.
EB: The data in the table should be exported successfully without any exception.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Export the data in the table.
3. Observe the exception being thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() function.
